The Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (HKSAR) is part of China's Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macao Greater Bay Area (GBA). The "InnoBay 2022" special program, presented by CGTN and the Hong Kong X Foundation, offers an in-depth look at how Hong Kong is transforming into a global hub for innovation and cutting-edge technology. It helps viewers worldwide better understand the innovation potential of the GBA and especially Hong Kong. CGTN hears from leading policymakers, scientists, investors and young entrepreneurs to get their take on the massive opportunities in the region and more.